      "Using data from unverified third-party websites without tracing to primary source. Several websites scrape exchange data with errors or significant lags. A revenue figure on a casual aggregator site may differ from the exchange filing because of classification differences (e.g., gross vs net revenue). Always verify material numbers against the company's exchange filing.",
